Before exclusion we have 70 subject_ids. We now exclude participants who have more than 10 missed trials, more than 10 consecutive left or right responses, or fewer than 56 trials recorded. Our final participant list contains 40 participants.

Response times

Participants make four responses on a trial, choosing a gamble and indicating how responsible each of the players was for the decision.
